**F006**
Severity: HIGH  
Category: design-concern  
Type: defect_fix  
Before-behavior: 涉及 threshold / fallback / lifecycle 的公共变更，应有 Contract Pack 约束 `invariants / counter_examples / risk_modules / test_debt`，并映射到 verification。  
After-behavior: 当前计划完全缺失这套 Contract Pack，而正文又引入了多个高语义风险点。  
Evidence: 我对 plan、design、gates 检索 `invariant|counter_examples|risk_modules|test_debt` 没有命中；现有 gates 文件只有 gate 元数据，见 [2026-04-13-knowledge-graph-phase1-gates.json:1](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-13-knowledge-graph-phase1-gates.json#L1)。与此同时，计划显式引入了 cycle fallback、matching threshold、无 MCU fallback、startup lifecycle 等红旗模式，见 [plan:728](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-13-knowledge-graph-phase1-plan.md#L728)、[plan:980](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-13-knowledge-graph-phase1-plan.md#L980)、[plan:1052](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-13-knowledge-graph-phase1-plan.md#L1052)、[plan:1597](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-13-knowledge-graph-phase1-plan.md#L1597)、[plan:1657](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-13-knowledge-graph-phase1-plan.md#L1657)、[plan:2519](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-13-knowledge-graph-phase1-plan.md#L2519)。  
Impact: 风险分级没有可验证依据，高风险 public API 变更没有 `risk_modules` 覆盖，后续 code review 很难判定是 defect 还是 behavior drift。  
Repair hypothesis:  
1. 可能的修复方向是先补一份独立 Contract Pack，把 `sync_knowledge_on_startup -> compute_all_stats -> get_graph -> 前端着色/导航` 链路的不变量、反例、风险模块和验证映射补齐。  
2. 禁止的修复模式包括：把现有 Task 文案机械复制成 invariants、用泛化的 `risk_modules=knowledge_tree/*` 充数、只写 threshold/fallback 结论但不给 verification。  
3. requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate

